<plot>Chloe is a woman on the verge of a breakdown. She stumbles into an empty hotel room at the 777 motel in downtown Los Angeles. It is the same hotel she first visited when she first came to City of Angels. She is shell-shocked from her tumultuous day and now here in her motel room, wants to drown out her feelings in a flood of pills and alcohol. She unloads all of her possessions from her suitcase onto her bed and falls asleep. Eventually the hotel unfolds a metaphysical time warp whereby Chloe is eventually visited by her previous 'self' 7 years younger and her future 'self' 7 years older.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?006777</url></doc>
